706535f-a.title: Brooklyn: Rogers Avenue - Empire Boulevard
706535f-a.text:
Rogers Ave., and Empire Boulevard; a general view north west, about 1870.)
This picture includes properties of the Chadwick, Boyton, Needham, Horgan
and Miller families. At present (1936), Stoddard Place and Ludlow Place are
in this area.
About 1870.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
